title: Sen. Patrick Leahy (D-VT), "The Road Taken"
description:
Senator Patrick Leahy (D-VT) reflects on his nearly 50 years in the U.S. Senate and some of the legislation he's worked on.  He's interviewed by USA Today Bureau Chief Susan Page.
